        <item>
            <title>Elon Musk 提告 OpenAI 申紧急禁制令，促尽快阻止 OpenAI 专为牟利机构</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/01/elon-musk-files-for-injunction-to-halt-openais-transition-to-a-for-profit/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=elon-musk-files-for-injunction-to-halt-openais-transition-to-a-for-profit</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/01/elon-musk-files-for-injunction-to-halt-openais-transition-to-a-for-profit/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 15:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
